    {
      "id": "state-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 1560,
      "width": 1000,
      "height": 170,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1️⃣ Auth Context\n   • User state (id, email, role)\n   • JWT tokens (access: 4h, refresh: 7d)\n   • isAuthenticated flag\n\n2️⃣ Notification Context\n   • Всплывающие сообщения (success/error/warning/info)\n   • Auto-hide duration\n\n3️⃣ React Query\n   • Server state caching\n   • Auto refetch\n   • Optimistic updates\n\n4️⃣ Formik\n   • Form state management\n   • Yup валидация schemas\n   • Field-level errors",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 162,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [
        "state-mgmt"
      ],
      "frameId": "frame-frontend",
      "locked": false,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 354615342,
      "index": "ab",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "seed": 1,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768898530685,
      "link": null,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1️⃣ Auth Context\n   • User state (id, email, role)\n   • JWT tokens (access: 4h, refresh: 7d)\n   • isAuthenticated flag\n\n2️⃣ Notification Context\n   • Toast messages (success/error/warning/info)\n   • Auto-hide duration\n\n3️⃣ React Query\n   • Server state caching\n   • Auto refetch\n   • Optimistic updates\n\n4️⃣ Formik\n   • Form state management\n   • Yup validation schemas\n   • Field-level errors",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 0.5902777777777778
    },
