      "height": 100,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Axios Configuration:\n• Base URL: http://localhost:5001/api (dev) or relative (prod)\n• Request interceptor: Add JWT token to Authorization header\n• Response interceptor: Handle 401 errors, refresh token logic\n• Таймаут: 300000ms (5 min)\n• withCredentials: true",
