      "width": 460,
      "height": 320,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "/api/contacts [auth]:\n• CRUD + search\n• GET /by-phone/:phone, /by-email/:email\n• POST /import (Excel), GET /export\n\n/api/companies [auth]:\n• CRUD + search\n• GET /by-inn/:inn\n• POST /import, GET /export\n\n/api/nomenclature [auth]:\n• CRUD + categories\n• POST /sync-bitrix\n• POST /import\n\n/api/search [auth]:\n• POST /заявки (Elasticsearch)\n• Fallback на PostgreSQL\n\n/api/settings [auth]:\n• GET /, GET/:key, PUT/:key [admin]\n\n/api/sync-manager [admin]:\n• POST /run, /run-all, /retry-failed\n\n/api/diagnostic:\n• GET /health (публичный)\n• GET /database [admin]",
