    },
    {
      "id": "services-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1290,
      "y": 1470,
      "width": 1040,
      "height": 260,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "📝 ЗаявкаService:\n• валидацияЗаявка(), createЗаявка(), updateStatus()\n• copyЗаявка(), periodЗаявкаs()\n• DB-first architecture (PostgreSQL = ИСТОЧНИК ИСТИНЫ)\n\n🔗 Bitrix24Service:\n• createDeal(), updateDeal(), getDeal()\n• getProducts() [5-level search], getCompanies(), getContacts()\n• getDealCategories(), getDealStages(), getUsers()\n• Retry mechanism: 3 попыток с экспоненциальная задержка\n\n💾 CacheService (Кэш в Памяти, НЕ Redis!):\n• TTL: 30 min (products, companies), 2 hours (categories)\n• Паттерн ключа: bitrix24:dynamic-options:{source}:{hash}\n• In-process memory storage\n\n🔍 SearchService (Elasticsearch):\n• indexЗаявка(), fullTextSearch()\n• Fallback на PostgreSQL ILIKE\n\n🔄 SyncService:\n• syncToBitrix24(), syncFromBitrix24(), webhookHandler()\n• Error classification: network/api/валидация\n• Retry logic для retryable errors",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 252,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [
        "services"
      ],
      "frameId": "frame-backend",
      "locked": false,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 709085554,
      "index": "au",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "seed": 1,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768898530685,
      "link": null,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "📝 SubmissionService:\n• validateSubmission(), createSubmission(), updateStatus()\n• copySubmission(), periodSubmissions()\n• DB-first architecture (PostgreSQL = SOURCE OF TRUTH)\n\n🔗 Bitrix24Service:\n• createDeal(), updateDeal(), getDeal()\n• getProducts() [5-level search], getCompanies(), getContacts()\n• getDealCategories(), getDealStages(), getUsers()\n• Retry mechanism: 3 attempts с exponential backoff\n\n💾 CacheService (Memory Cache, NOT Redis!):\n• TTL: 30 min (products, companies), 2 hours (categories)\n• Key pattern: bitrix24:dynamic-options:{source}:{hash}\n• In-process memory storage\n\n🔍 SearchService (Elasticsearch):\n• indexSubmission(), fullTextSearch()\n• Fallback на PostgreSQL ILIKE\n\n🔄 SyncService:\n• syncToBitrix24(), syncFromBitrix24(), webhookHandler()\n• Error classification: network/api/validation\n• Retry logic для retryable errors",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 0.7738095238095238
    },
