      "type": "text",
      "x": 2490,
      "y": 745,
      "width": 410,
      "height": 150,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "📋 Форма:\nPK: id (UUID)\n• name (уникальный)\n• title, description\n• isActive\n• bitrixDealCategory\n• successMessage\n\nСвязи:\n→ OneToMany FormField (cascade delete)\n→ OneToMany Заявка",
      "textAlign": "left",
