      "originalText": "📋 Form:\nPK: id (UUID)\n• name (unique)\n• title, description\n• isActive\n• bitrixDealCategory\n• successMessage\n\nRelations:\n→ OneToMany FormField (cascade delete)\n→ OneToMany Submission",
      "autoResize": true,
