    {
      "id": "submission-entity-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3010,
      "y": 515,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 710,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "📄 Заявка (CORE):\nPK: id (UUID)\nFK: formId → Form\nFK: userId → User (nullable)\nFK: assignedToId → User (nullable)\n• submissionNumber (уникальный, auto)\n• title, status\n• priority (low/medium/high/urgent)\n\n🔗 Bitrix24 Sync:\n• bitrixDealId\n• bitrixCategoryId\n• bitrixSyncStatus (pending/synced/failed)\n• bitrixSyncError, bitrixSyncedAt\n• bitrixSyncAttempts\n\n📦 Data:\n• formData (JSONB) ← Main data\n• notes, tags (text[])\n\n📊 Denormalized (performance):\n• formName, formTitle\n• userEmail, userName\n• assignedToName\n\n📈 Precomputed (analytics):\n• dayOfWeek, monthOfYear\n• yearCreated\n• processingTimeMinutes\n\n🔄 Периодические заявки:\n• isPeriodЗаявка\n• periodGroupId, periodStartDate\n• periodEndDate, periodPosition\n\nИндексы: submissionNumber (уникальный),\n        (status, createdAt),\n        (userId, status),\n        (bitrixSyncStatus),\n        (priority, status), tags",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 702,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [
        "database"
      ],
      "frameId": "frame-database",
      "containerId": "submission-entity-box",
      "locked": false,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 653167602,
      "index": "b06",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "seed": 1,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768898530685,
      "link": null,
      "originalText": "📄 Submission (CORE):\nPK: id (UUID)\nFK: formId → Form\nFK: userId → User (nullable)\nFK: assignedToId → User (nullable)\n• submissionNumber (unique, auto)\n• title, status\n• priority (low/medium/high/urgent)\n\n🔗 Bitrix24 Sync:\n• bitrixDealId\n• bitrixCategoryId\n• bitrixSyncStatus (pending/synced/failed)\n• bitrixSyncError, bitrixSyncedAt\n• bitrixSyncAttempts\n\n📦 Data:\n• formData (JSONB) ← Main data\n• notes, tags (text[])\n\n📊 Denormalized (performance):\n• formName, formTitle\n• userEmail, userName\n• assignedToName\n\n📈 Precomputed (analytics):\n• dayOfWeek, monthOfYear\n• yearCreated\n• processingTimeMinutes\n\n🔄 Period Submissions:\n• isPeriodSubmission\n• periodGroupId, periodStartDate\n• periodEndDate, periodPosition\n\nIndices: submissionNumber (unique),\n        (status, createdAt),\n        (userId, status),\n        (bitrixSyncStatus),\n        (priority, status), tags",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.3653846153846154
    },
