      "originalText": "Other Entities:\n\n🏢 Company (id, name, inn, kpp, ogrn, legalAddress, phone, email, bitrixCompanyId, searchVector GIN)\n👤 Contact (id, companyId→Company, name, position, phone, email, bitrixContactId)\n📦 Nomenclature (id, name, category→NomenclatureCategory, unit→Unit, price, bitrixProductId)\n📂 NomenclatureCategory (id, name, parentId)\n📏 NomenclatureUnit (id, name, code)\n⚙️ Settings (id, key unique, value JSONB, category, isPublic, isEncrypted)\n🔄 SubmissionHistory (id, submissionId→Submission, actionType, description, changes JSONB)\n📅 SubmissionPeriodGroup (id, name, startDate, endDate, frequency)\n⏰ ScheduledSubmission (id, periodGroupId, scheduledDate, status)\n🔄 SyncMetadata (id, entityType, entityId, lastSyncAt, syncStatus)",
