      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "📞 API Методы:\n\n• createDeal(dealData) → dealId, categoryId\n  POST /rest/{webhook}/crm.deal.add\n\n• updateDeal(dealId, data) → success\n  POST /rest/{webhook}/crm.deal.update\n\n• getProducts(search, categoryId) → products[] [5-уровневая Стратегия Поиска]:\n  1️⃣ Поиск по ID (if query is number)\n  2️⃣ Точное совпадение имени (NAME = query)\n  3️⃣ Частичное совпадение имени (NAME LIKE %query%)\n  4️⃣ Поиск в описании (DESCRIPTION LIKE %query%)\n  5️⃣ Нечёткое совпадение слов (split query, filter client-side)\n  💾 Кэш: 30 мин TTL\n\n• getCompanies(search, filter) → companies[]\n  Search by: name, INN\n  💾 Кэш: 30 мин TTL\n\n• getContacts(search, companyId) → contacts[]\n  Search by: name, phone, email\n  💾 Кэш: 30 мин TTL\n\n• getDealCategories() → categories[]\n  💾 Кэш: 2 hours TTL\n\n• getDealStages(categoryId) → stages[]\n  💾 Кэш: 1 hour TTL\n\n🔁 Механизм Повтора: 3 попыток с экспоненциальная задержка\n⏱️ Таймаут: 15 секунд на запрос",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 412,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [
        "integrations"
      ],
      "frameId": "frame-integrations",
      "locked": false,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 258268850,
      "index": "b0E",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "seed": 1,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768898575974,
      "link": null,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "📞 API Methods:\n\n• createDeal(dealData) → dealId, categoryId\n  POST /rest/{webhook}/crm.deal.add\n\n• updateDeal(dealId, data) → success\n  POST /rest/{webhook}/crm.deal.update\n\n• getProducts(search, categoryId) → products[] [5-Level Search Strategy]:\n  1️⃣ Search by ID (if query is number)\n  2️⃣ Exact name match (NAME = query)\n  3️⃣ Partial name (NAME LIKE %query%)\n  4️⃣ Description search (DESCRIPTION LIKE %query%)\n  5️⃣ Fuzzy word match (split query, filter client-side)\n  💾 Cache: 30 min TTL\n\n• getCompanies(search, filter) → companies[]\n  Search by: name, INN\n  💾 Cache: 30 min TTL\n\n• getContacts(search, companyId) → contacts[]\n  Search by: name, phone, email\n  💾 Cache: 30 min TTL\n\n• getDealCategories() → categories[]\n  💾 Cache: 2 hours TTL\n\n• getDealStages(categoryId) → stages[]\n  💾 Cache: 1 hour TTL\n\n🔁 Retry Mechanism: 3 attempts с exponential backoff\n⏱️ Timeout: 15 seconds per request",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 0.9375
    },
