      "type": "text",
      "x": 3540,
      "y": 995,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 170,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "🗺️ Маппинг Полей:\n\nFormField.bitrixFieldId →\n  Bitrix24 Custom Field\n\nExamples:\n• UF_CRM_XXX → Custom field\n• CONTACT_ID → Contact binding\n• COMPANY_ID → Company binding\n• PRODUCT_ROWS → Products table\n• TITLE → Deal title\n• STAGE_ID → Deal stage",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 162,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
