      "updated": 1768898530685,
      "link": null,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🗺️ Field Mapping:\n\nFormField.bitrixFieldId →\n  Bitrix24 Custom Field\n\nExamples:\n• UF_CRM_XXX → Custom field\n• CONTACT_ID → Contact binding\n• COMPANY_ID → Company binding\n• PRODUCT_ROWS → Products table\n• TITLE → Deal title\n• STAGE_ID → Deal stage",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.0119047619047619
