    {
      "id": "elasticsearch-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3540,
      "y": 1520,
      "width": 1010,
      "height": 170,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Индекс: заявки\n\nИндексированные Поля:\n• submissionNumber, title\n• formData (nested)\n• userName, userEmail\n• status, priority, tags\n• createdAt\n\nФункции Поиска:\n• Полнотекстовый поиск\n• Многополевой поиск\n• Нечёткое совпадение\n• Агрегации (status, priority)\n\n⚠️ Резервный вариант: Если ES недоступен → PostgreSQL ILIKE поиск",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 162,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [
        "integrations"
      ],
      "frameId": "frame-integrations",
      "locked": false,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1901980594,
      "index": "b0O",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "seed": 1,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768898530685,
      "link": null,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Index: submissions\n\nIndexed Fields:\n• submissionNumber, title\n• formData (nested)\n• userName, userEmail\n• status, priority, tags\n• createdAt\n\nSearch Features:\n• Full-text search\n• Multi-field search\n• Fuzzy matching\n• Aggregations (status, priority)\n\n⚠️ Fallback: If ES unavailable → PostgreSQL ILIKE search",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 0.6640625
    },
