    {
      "id": "roles-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2770,
      "y": 4170,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 40,
      "fontSize": 32,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "👥 Роли пользователей",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 34,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [
        "roles"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "locked": false,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 2052274734,
      "index": "b0t",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "seed": 1,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768898530685,
      "link": null,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "👥 User Roles",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "roles-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2770,
      "y": 4220,
      "width": 960,
      "height": 310,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "👤 Роль USER:\nРазрешения:\n  ✓ View Главная страница (form)\n  ✓ Отправить forms (POST /api/forms/submit)\n  ✓ View own заявки (GET /api/заявки/my)\n  ✓ Edit own заявки\n  ✓ Copy own заявки\n  ✓ Cancel own заявки\n  ✗ Cannot access Страница Администратора\n  ✗ Cannot manage users\n  ✗ Cannot edit forms\n\n👨‍💼 Роль ADMIN:\nРазрешения:\n  ✓ Все разрешения USER\n  ✓ Access Страница Администратора (7 вкладок)\n  ✓ Управление формами (CRUD)\n  ✓ Управление пользователями (CRUD)\n  ✓ View all заявки\n  ✓ Управление номенклатурой, companies, contacts\n  ✓ Configure Интеграция Bitrix24\n  ✓ Системные настройки\n  ✓ Экспорт/Импорт data\n  ✓ Force sync to Bitrix24\n  ✓ View diagnostic info\n  ✓ Dashboard analytics",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 302,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "groupIds": [
        "roles"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "locked": false,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1933002674,
      "index": "b0u",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "seed": 1,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768898530685,
      "link": null,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "👤 USER Role:\nPermissions:\n  ✓ View HomePage (form)\n  ✓ Submit forms (POST /api/forms/submit)\n  ✓ View own submissions (GET /api/submissions/my)\n  ✓ Edit own submissions\n  ✓ Copy own submissions\n  ✓ Cancel own submissions\n  ✗ Cannot access AdminPage\n  ✗ Cannot manage users\n  ✗ Cannot edit forms\n\n👨‍💼 ADMIN Role:\nPermissions:\n  ✓ All USER permissions\n  ✓ Access AdminPage (7 tabs)\n  ✓ Manage forms (CRUD)\n  ✓ Manage users (CRUD)\n  ✓ View all submissions\n  ✓ Manage nomenclature, companies, contacts\n  ✓ Configure Bitrix24 integration\n  ✓ System settings\n  ✓ Export/Import data\n  ✓ Force sync to Bitrix24\n  ✓ View diagnostic info\n  ✓ Dashboard analytics",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 0.7451923076923077
    },
